snippet.title: Ale & Tale Tavern Final Trailer
snippet.description:
A cozy coop first-person fantasy tavern simulator where players cook different dishes and feed visitors.You are in for a stunning mix of genres: a coop first-person fantasy tavern simulator in an open world, action, fishing, hunting, exploration, fun and diverse quests. And, of course, COOKING! Play solo or with friends and feed the entire world!

Buy it on Steam: https://s.team/a/2683150/
https://scienartgames.com/
